devil: devil (A cross-platform image library)
devil:
devil: Developer's Image Library (DevIL) is a programmer's library to develop
devil: applications with very powerful image loading capabilities, yet is
devil: easy for a developer to learn and use. Ultimate control of images is
devil: left to the developer, so unnecessary conversions, etc. are not
devil: performed. DevIL utilizes a simple, yet powerful, syntax. DevIL can
devil: load, save, convert, manipulate, filter and display a wide variety of
devil: image formats.
devil: http://openil.sourceforge.net/
